snippet.title: R-Tuned Ultimate Street Racing - Battle Mode Gameplay
snippet.description:
Gameplay of R-Tuned Ultimate Street Racing arcade machine by Sega. The video, captured straight from the machine's gameboard in store at Highway Entertainment, shows the driving arcade game being played in Battle mode.

For further information on this arcade machine please visit http://www.arcade-game-sales.com/products/r-tuned-racing-arcade-machine/9991.html
